subject: libXinerama should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.
commitMessage:
libXinerama should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.

_____________|______________
succeeded    | succeeded
excluded     | excluded
broken       |
failed       |
unresolvable |
blocked      |
locked       |
note:

      allowed for OBS administration.
